{"tid":1068792,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"九旬婆婆首置客掀熱話 親屬破頂價沽出東港城","createTime":"2019-03-19T13:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T13:51:10.000Z","uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef061dcf61975aa412550f567704191310a1b13","tid":1068792,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/九旬婆婆首置客掀熱話-親屬破頂價沽出東港城/ar-BBUWOAu?ocid=spartanntp_edu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Flocalnews%2F%E4%B9%9D%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%86%E5%A9%86%E9%A6%96%E7%BD%AE%E5%AE%A2%E6%8E%80%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E8%A6%AA%E5%B1%AC%E7%A0%B4%E9%A0%82%E5%83%B9%E6%B2%BD%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%B1%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%2Far-BBUWOAu%3Focid%3Dspartanntp_edu&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=cfb58335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/九旬婆婆首置客掀熱話-親屬破頂價沽出東港城/ar-BBUWOAu?ocid=spartanntp_edu</a><br />\n<br />\n九旬婆婆首置客掀熱話 親屬破頂價沽出東港城 <br />\n<br />\n流動新聞 港聞 6 小時前 <br />\n<br />\n去年底觀塘樓盤「凱滙」銷售時，98歲婆婆鄧碧雲以首置身份、斥資1,949萬元入市，甚受關注。據了解，她的一名親屬所持有的將軍澳東港城複式連天台戶，近日以1,800萬元易手，成交價創屋苑新高。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8n2KpR1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8n2KpR1.jpg&h=d7d5b10f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n98歲婆婆鄧碧雲以首置身份買新樓，一度成為市場焦點。（網絡圖片）<br />\n <br />\n據報單位原業主為李兆青及陳詠梅，<span style=\"color: red;\">二人2006年9月以651萬元買入，帳面獲利約1,148萬元。</span><br />\n鄧氏於2013年以逾1837萬元購入黃大仙現崇山2座中層戶，當時報稱居於東港城，即今次錄得成交的單位。鄧婆婆其後就現崇山單位向銀行承做按揭，東港城物業持有人之一李兆青被列為借款人。其後，鄧婆婆透過內部轉讓現崇山物業「甩名」，換取首置客身分，而當時轉到東港城物業持有人陳詠梅名下。"},{"pid":"9d49f73c8191adf2b94c5a185b00ce7ad6ea14b5","tid":1068792,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeDJFqW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeDJFqW.png&h=ae99fe86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6bd66d33585f3858e08bd29fe403a28093f2b56","tid":1068792,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"呀麻 我係你個孫"},{"pid":"2afff2340ef548c34fe751b983db152249fa0ab2","tid":1068792,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"首先你要有個98歲阿婆"}]}